N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 400.17 - Reports of tests of pressure compensated counters

State Regulations
A report of all installation tests, office tests, periodic
tests, and complaint tests made during each year shall be prepared as of

December 31st of that year. Such report shall be made in a form satisfactory to
the commission and shall be filed with the commission not later than January
31st following the date of the report. Notes
